title: Volleyball Top Five
text: Chap Carter & Mike Williams NCPrivateSchoolSports.com Providence Day School defeated an ever-improving Charlotte Latin squad in a 3-2 thriller on Senior Night at PD. PD Chargers have one more match and that is with Asheville School at CCDS gym. With wins over all 3A opponents outside the conference plus victories over Covenant Day and Cannon plus two over Latin, the Chargers are sitting pretty for a possible top four seed in the playoffs. The committee will meet next Sunday to decide the 12-team playoff field. ... More ... To continue reading this article you must be a member. Sign Up Now!
